Feature: Search for content by keyword without valid API key (UC001)

  In order to authenticate DPLA API users
  API users must have a valid API key

  Scenario: Basic keyword search without API key
    When I search for "banana"
      And do not provide an API key
    Then the API should return an error

    Scenario: Basic keyword search with invalid API key
      When I search for "banana"
        And provide an invalid API key
      Then the API should return an error

